Package net.heroicefforts.viable.android.rep.it.gdata Description

Google provides Gdata client libraries in Java for interacting with the Issue Tracker. However, these do not seem to play in Android. So, I've taken a loose shadow interpretation of the Gdata classes with enough functionality to meet the needs of this application.
